description: Gladion confirmed that it was Lusamine`s when it was sent out to battle against them in the Ultra Deep Sea. It had an aura being emitting from its body because the Ultra Beast Nihilego was controlling it. Kiawe`s Turtonator and Kiawe`s Marowak battled Salazzle to let the other go after Lusamine.
name: Ennewt (Lusamine)
